Requirements:
Apache+MySQL+PHP

Installation instructions:

1. copy or link Zend framework to library/Zend
2. install database from MOR project (no changes needed. if you don't know what it is, ask Alex ;))
2.5. You can use the mysql dump application/scripts/iso11179.sql
3. modify configs/application.ini (modify resources.db.*)
4. enjoy

Search:

Implemented with Zend's Lucene port. 
* Features:
	1. Keyword search(case sensitive): The following query will search only in Definitions: "Definition:mydefinition". The keywords are taken from the DB
	2. See query language documentation for complete list of features. http://framework.zend.com/manual/en/zend.search.lucene.query-language.html
	3. To rebuild and optimize the search index execute "{baseurl}/Index/updatesearchindex" in your browser